text: Zöe Elizabeth LuckerEngland & Wales births 1837-2006 (born 11 April 1974) is an English actress. She is best known for portraying the roles of Tanya Turner in the ITV drama series Footballers' Wives (2002–2006), Vanessa Gold in the BBC soap opera EastEnders (2010–2011), Carol Barry in the BBC school-based drama series Waterloo Road (2013–2014), and Reenie McQueen in the Channel 4 soap opera Hollyoaks (2015–2016). ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:Actors from Yorkshire Category:People from Huddersfield
